 Unit 1.3 — Laws of Thermodynamics, Heat Transfer, Mass & Energy Transfer, and Material Balance

Think of this topic as answering one big question: **How does energy and matter move around in the environment?** Everything from why the Earth is warm, to how pollutants spread in the atmosphere, to how sewage treatment works — it all comes back to these fundamental laws.

